Paper: 14107168
Title: A supersymmetric reduction on the three-sphere
Authors: Nihat Sadik Deger and Henning Samtleben and Ozgur Sarioglu and Dieter Van den Bleeken
Abstract: We present the embedding of three-dimensional SO(4)$\ltimes\mathbb{R}^6$ gauged $N=4$ supergravity with quaternionic target space SO(4,4)$/$(SO(4)$\times$SO(4)) into $D=6$, $N=(1,0)$ supergravity coupled to a single chiral tensor multiplet through a consistent reduction on AdS$_3\times S^3$.
